<!-- BODY -->
<table class="body-wrap" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 100%; margin: 0; background-color:#f5f5f5; padding: 0;">
  <tr style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;"></td>
    <td class="container" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; display: block !important; border-radius:3px; clear: both !important; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0;">

      <div class="content" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; display: block; margin: 0 auto; padding: 15px;">
        <table style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; width: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><tr style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
          <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; padding: 0;">

            <p class="lead" style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Dear Snapmail User,</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Firstly, you may have got a blank email from us this morning - Sorry, we were preparing for this mailshot and pressed send too quickly. The message I wanted to deliver is the following:</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Until today, these emails have come from support@evercam.io but future emails will come from snapmail@evercam.io.</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">We're doing this so we can implement a nice new ticketing system on the old address.</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">For 95% of you, this will make no difference, but some of you may have a firewall or other email handling rule to change. If you are using Snapmail to send images directly to folders in Procore, ViewPoint or any other Project Management Software you may need to make a minor change to the Rule you set up for this.</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">If you find you're not getting expected Snapmails, or have any other questions, you can reply to this email or call me on the number below. You are welcome to put me directly in touch with your IT support team.</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Again, sorry for the double email, the relevant person has been shot. ;)</p>
           <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Yours,</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 0px; padding: 0;"><b style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:arial">Marco Herbst</b></p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.0; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">Director | +353 86 1960451</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.0; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;">www.evercam.io</p>
            <p style="line-height: 1.0; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 0;"><font color="#d61d3b" style="font-size:small;font-family:arial,sans-serif">EVER</font><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size:small;font-family:arial,sans-serif">CAM - Construction Time-lapse</span><span style="font-size:small;font-family:arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span></font></p>
            <br>

          </td>
        </tr></table></div><!-- /content -->

